    "created_at": "2013-12-07T06:22:53Z",
    "updated_at": "2013-12-07T06:22:53Z",
    "body": "This was closed by #10804 now that we're no longer calling `dup` on all the stdio file descriptors on linux/max. We're still required to do it on windows, but that's a libuv limitation. Next time libuv is updated, that's something to watch for.\n",
